---
---

<section id="about" class="about-section tile-bg-1">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="about-grid reveal">
      <div class="about-statement">
        <h2 class="display-lg statement-text">
          Bridging science and code to build <span class="white-text">fast, intuitive web experiences</span>.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="about-details">
        <p class="body-copy text-block">
          I'm Aman Verma, a science student with a deep interest in how things work—especially on the web. I enjoy building modern websites, useful web tools, and responsive applications from scratch.
        </p>
        
        <p class="body-copy text-block">
          For me, development is all about the details. I focus on crafting clean interfaces, optimizing performance, and ensuring solid user experience and SEO. I want everything I build to feel fast and natural to use.
        </p>
        
        <p class="body-copy text-block text-muted">
          I continuously learn new technologies by building real projects. My long-term goal is to become a skilled full-stack developer and build products that solve real-world problems.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 45% 50%;
    gap: 5%;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .statement-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .white-text {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .text-block {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .text-block strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .text-muted {
    color: var(--color-text-muted-dark);
  }

  /* Responsive styles */
  @media (max-width: 834px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    }
    
    .statement-text {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
